    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish and zero imperfections, while the interior still retains that new-car smell with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, with a complete service history and all original components in perfect working order. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that remains in 'as-new' condition, requiring nothing but a new home.",
