    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system to achieve a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis dynamics are maintained by a factory-spec M-variable differential lock and an aluminum multi-link rear suspension setup, ensuring optimal lateral grip and power delivery. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, addressing the primary mechanical concerns of this platform. The 6-speed manual transmission offers short, precise throws, perfectly complementing the hydraulic steering rack's communicative feedback. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain integrity and longitudinal acceleration remain uncompromised.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs smoothly. Serious buyers only.",
