    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It's got plenty of life left in it and handles like a dream. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable car without the 'new car' price tag. Come take it for a spin!",
