    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain sends power through an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on structural integrity, including a reinforced rear subframe. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and VANOS inspection to ensure the high-pressure oil system operates within factory spec. Riding on a refreshed suspension with upgraded bushings, this driver\u2019s car offers the mechanical purity and hydraulic steering feedback the E46 is celebrated for.",
